46.
No 75/CF/52.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SEC RETARIAT
New Delhi, the 26th November, 1954.
The undersigned is directed to inform all Members of
the Council of Ministers that Shri Ajit Prasad Jain
assumed
office as Minister in-charge of the Food & Agriculture
Ministry with effect from Thursday, the 25th November, 1954.
He will continue to be in-charge of the Rehabilitation
Ministry also.
(A.S. Cill)
for Secretary to the Cabinet.
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the Presi dent/the
Private Secretary to the Vice-President/the Special Assistant
to the Prime Minister/the Principal Private Secretary to the
Prime Minister, for information.
(A.S. G111)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
